section.heading: High-Need Healthcare Career Scholarships and Supports Program.

annotations.annotation: For temporary (90 days) creation of this section, see § 102 of High Need Healthcare Career Scholarship and Health Professional Loan Repayment Program Emergency Amendment Act of 2022 (D.C. Act 24-468, July 6, 2022, 69 DCR 008390).

For temporary (225 days) creation of this section, see § 102 of High Need Healthcare Career Scholarship and Health Professional Loan Repayment Program Temporary Amendment Act of 2022 (D.C. Law 24-184, Sept. 21, 2022, 0 DCR 0).

Applicability of D.C. Law 24-313: § 301 of D.C. Law 24-313 provided that the creation of this section by § 102 of D.C. Law 24-313 is subject to the inclusion of the law’s fiscal effect in an approved budget and financial plan. Therefore that amendment has not been implemented.
